{"pagelen": 100, "values": [{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-gui/issues/5/comments/40158099.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-gui/issues/5#comment-40158099"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-gui/issues/5.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 5, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-gui.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-gui"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{d80b97c2-f3f9-42b2-86b0-8c1fd4aa845f}ts=1406854"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "ign-gui", "full_name": "ignitionrobotics/ign-gui", "uuid": "{d80b97c2-f3f9-42b2-86b0-8c1fd4aa845f}"}, "title": "Allow to choose the widgets that can be added to a window via menu option"}, "content": {"raw": "How about offering the following options in the configuration file:\n\n~~~\n<window>\n  <menus>\n    <!-- Set hide to true to hide plugins menu, visible by default -->\n    <plugins hide=\"true\">\n\n      <!-- Set enable to false to prevent any path lookup. In that case, \n           unless there are plugins given by <plugin> tags, the menu will be empty. -->\n      <paths enable=\"false\">\n\n        <!-- Set to false not to list plugins from paths given by the `IGN_GUI_PLUGIN_PATH` variable -->\n        <env_var>false</env_var>\n\n        <!-- Set to false not to list plugins from paths added by the `ignition::gui::addPluginPath` API call -->\n        <api>false</api>\n\n        <!-- Set to false not to list plugins from the default path ~/.ignition/gui/plugins -->\n        <default>false</default>\n\n        <!-- Set to false not to list plugins distributed with Ignition GUI -->\n        <canonical>false</canonical>\n\n      </paths>\n\n    <!-- Plugins given by <plugin> tags will be listed above all plugins found in paths. \n        Note that Ignition GUI still needs to find these plugins within one of the 4\n        paths given above even if all paths are hidden. -->\n    <plugin name=\"Publisher\"mailto:cen.aguero@gmail.com\">&#99;&#101;&#110;&#46;&#97;&#103;&#117;&#101;&#114;&#111;&#64;&#103;&#109;&#97;&#105;&#108;&#46;&#99;&#111;&#109;</a></p>\n<p>\u2192 &lt;&lt;cset <a href=\"#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-gui/commits/8e01ea1a25e0\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">8e01ea1a25e0</a>&gt;&gt;</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2017-11-08T22:24:54.188973+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Louise Poubel", "uuid": "{5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:6ff86fcb-b7ab-44a5-b8a6-f6d9cae8b6e8/7d903d90-c5ea-4182-b7ef-0d467e9e1c74/128"}}, "nickname": "chapulina", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:6ff86fcb-b7ab-44a5-b8a6-f6d9cae8b6e8"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 41094078}], "page": 1, "size": 10}